WEBVTT

00:01.335 --> 00:03.645
Narrator:
In New York City war on crime

00:03.670 --> 00:07.379
the worst criminal offenders
are pursued by the detectives

00:07.407 --> 00:08.977
of the Major Case Squad.

00:09.009 --> 00:11.489
These are their stories.

00:13.180 --> 00:15.160
Girl: So Brittany's like, committed.

00:15.182 --> 00:17.389
Who knows if she's even going to show up.

00:17.417 --> 00:20.489
That's not even the point. Who is this guy?

00:20.521 --> 00:24.663
All of a sudden he's supposed
to be in Atlanta for an Elton John benefit.

00:24.691 --> 00:27.501
He is off of the VIP list forever.

00:29.863 --> 00:31.809
Lilly, I need to speak with you.

00:31.832 --> 00:33.778
We're late, Daddy.

00:35.035 --> 00:36.241
This article?

00:36.270 --> 00:38.511
Lilly: Dad, that's great exposure.

00:38.539 --> 00:40.519
That's a national magazine.

00:40.541 --> 00:42.578
Didn't you get enough exposure last summer

00:42.609 --> 00:44.680
when you nearly ran over those people?

00:44.711 --> 00:48.523
- Yeah, by accident.
- And now this-- this exposé of your sex life?

00:49.716 --> 00:51.855
Nobody takes that stuff seriously.

00:51.885 --> 00:55.264
They do, Lilly. It's degrading.

00:57.224 --> 00:59.830
Well, I didn't do it to embarrass you, okay?

01:00.994 --> 01:03.975
- Let's talk about this later.
- Where are you going?

01:03.997 --> 01:06.443
- Where do you think?
- I don't want you going there.

01:06.466 --> 01:09.140
I know what goes on there.
That so-called friend of yours,

01:09.169 --> 01:10.876
if he doesn't stay away from you--

01:10.904 --> 01:13.817
- Daddy, stop it!
- Lilly, I mean it.

01:13.840 --> 01:15.842
I can hurt him.

01:20.847 --> 01:23.054
Lilly, I’m on your side.

01:23.083 --> 01:25.962
Sometimes I wish you'd remember that.

01:32.693 --> 01:36.231
Does it ever occur to your dad
what a supreme geek he is?

01:36.263 --> 01:38.675
Don't say that. Well, he is.

01:38.699 --> 01:40.872
Well, shut up, Serena.

01:44.171 --> 01:46.014
( techno music playing )

01:47.874 --> 01:49.876
Man: You need to get out of there.

01:49.910 --> 01:52.891
- 'Cause that is out of control.
- He was threatening me.

01:52.913 --> 01:54.722
I was like, "Oh, that's great, Daddy.

01:54.748 --> 01:56.489
Real warm and fuzzy. I love you, too."

01:56.516 --> 01:58.689
You want me to do a Menendez on him?

01:58.719 --> 02:00.528
Just say the word, I’m there for you.

02:00.554 --> 02:02.329
Thank you, sweetie.

02:05.993 --> 02:07.666
Hey, jerkwad!

02:07.694 --> 02:09.833
Put it away, Eddie.

02:13.166 --> 02:14.736
I'm sorry, man, I got this.

02:14.768 --> 02:17.806
Go tell Jimmy I said
take care of you, all right?

02:17.838 --> 02:20.717
Try that again, I'm not
letting you back in here.

02:25.679 --> 02:28.785
- How you ladies doing?
- Great.

02:28.815 --> 02:31.819
'Cause we've only been here a half hour.

02:31.852 --> 02:33.695
Where have you been?

02:34.855 --> 02:37.028
Come on, I want to talk to you.

02:44.698 --> 02:46.735
Where'd you go to?

02:50.203 --> 02:52.479
Let's have some fun.

02:54.000 --> 03:00.074
